description: Puma Exploration Inc., a junior mining exploration company, acquires, explores for, and develops mining properties in Canada. The company explores for gold, silver, and copper deposits. Its flagship project is the Williams Brook Gold project covering an area of approximately 20,662 hectares located in New Brunswick. The company is headquartered in Rimouski, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Marcel  Robillard Geo., M.Sc., P.Geo.
